platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Inspiration tends to strike when you least expect itheck, some of our best ideas come to us in the showerand Procreate is a dazzling way to snatch sparks of visual genius out of the ether and bring them to life. Behind the apps slick drawing and painting tools are robust features that youd expect from a full-fledged illustration packageit even has the ingenious ability to use your Apple Watch as a color palette picker. If a brilliant notion does strike in the shower, though, get out and dry off.
